description: This file defines a React component 'ProductList' that renders a table displaying a list of products with their current prices, previous prices, and percentage changes. It includes helper functions like 'percentChange' to calculate price differences, and handles loading, error, and empty states. The component also supports actions such as selecting a product and deleting it.

methods.name: percentChange(current, last)
methods.description: Calculates the percentage change between the last and current prices.

methods.name: ProductList({ loading, error, products = [], onSelect, onDelete, })
methods.description: React component that renders a list of products in a table with options to view, select, and delete products.
